definition:
Someone descended from Caleb who was a man living at the time of Egypt and Wilderness and Israel before the Monarchy, first mentioned at Num.13.6; 
 son of: Jephunneh (H3312); 
 brother of: Kenaz (H7073I); 
 father of: Achsah (H5915), Iru (H5900), Elah (H0425J), Naam (H5277)
Group of ka.lev (כָּלֵב "Caleb" H3612) 
 § Calebite, of Caleb "dog"
 a descendant of Caleb
